<subSubSection id="90F56566C74AFFB4FF37FEF33858FECE" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="D85036EDC74AFFB4FF37FEF33858FECE" blockId="23.[151,1436,152,588]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis id="EA9BEAFFC74AFFB4FF37FEF33811FEA8" bold="true" box="[197,366,263,289]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Distribution.</emphasis>
The western Sonoran Desert, Mojave Desert and northern California into Oregon and Washington.
</paragraph>
